Tavatron jumped slightly when Dinobot snarled at her:

"Sorry, I didn't mean to take you by surprise. I'm not used to making my 
presence known before I enter a room." Tavatron looked at the comp screen, a 
million battle tactics in preparation for the coming battle raced through 
her mind:

Tavatron pointed at a name on the screen:

"There, that 'Transantulus' he's new. A former Pred I think, maybe Alliance, 
I'm not sure." Tavatron looked over at Dinobot, waiting for his response.
